WEBVTT

00:00:00.440 --> 00:00:03.869
Good morning, family. I'm going to

00:00:03.879 --> 00:00:06.789
talk to you all about what's on

00:00:06.799 --> 00:00:07.869
my heart and what I've been praying

00:00:07.879 --> 00:00:10.350
about. You know the things I've

00:00:10.360 --> 00:00:14.910
seen whenever I pray.

00:00:14.920 --> 00:00:16.349
People are asking me what I feel

00:00:16.359 --> 00:00:18.310
about what's going on with Israel and

00:00:18.320 --> 00:00:21.910
Iran right now. This is exactly what

00:00:21.920 --> 00:00:24.870
I tried to tell you all in

00:00:24.870 --> 00:00:24.880
March—it

00:00:24.880 --> 00:00:28.429
was

00:00:28.439 --> 00:00:31.230
probably the end of February—whenever the

00:00:31.240 --> 00:00:34.470
Lord told me that the month of April, during the

00:00:34.470 --> 00:00:34.480
eclipse, would

00:00:34.480 --> 00:00:36.430
be significant. I said

00:00:36.440 --> 00:00:38.750
nothing would happen during the eclipse,

00:00:38.760 --> 00:00:40.950
but after the eclipse,

00:00:40.960 --> 00:00:44.110
because of Passover,

00:00:44.120 --> 00:00:46.590
there would be an

00:00:46.600 --> 00:00:50.510
acceleration of war,

00:00:50.520 --> 00:00:53.110
weather

00:00:53.110 --> 00:00:53.120
events,

00:00:53.120 --> 00:00:56.990
financial issues,

00:00:56.990 --> 00:00:57.000
and

00:00:57.000 --> 00:00:59.590
signs in the heavens.

00:00:59.600 --> 00:01:00.470
The

00:01:00.480 --> 00:01:02.310
Lord

00:01:02.320 --> 00:01:04.390
told

00:01:04.400 --> 00:01:07.310
me back during Rosh Hashanah—and I'll repeat

00:01:07.320 --> 00:01:09.510
myself

00:01:09.520 --> 00:01:12.630
again—that

00:01:12.640 --> 00:01:15.030
from Rosh Hashanah to Rosh Hashanah, things would accelerate

00:01:15.030 --> 00:01:15.040
and

00:01:15.040 --> 00:01:17.149
almost double in the

00:01:17.159 --> 00:01:19.749
spirit realm.

00:01:19.759 --> 00:01:22.109
Then He came back to me and told

00:01:22.119 --> 00:01:24.950
me it would happen again during

00:01:24.960 --> 00:01:27.310
Passover and that things would

00:01:27.320 --> 00:01:29.109
accelerate even more. This

00:01:29.119 --> 00:01:32.310
was concerning red heifer things

00:01:32.310 --> 00:01:32.320
that

00:01:32.320 --> 00:01:35.149
were going to escalate because of this.

00:01:35.159 --> 00:01:38.109
Here we are; it's happening right

00:01:38.119 --> 00:01:40.670
before our faces. All this stuff is

00:01:40.680 --> 00:01:43.310
happening on the news, and it's

00:01:43.320 --> 00:01:46.830
a big deal. I was interceding for it,

00:01:46.840 --> 00:01:49.350
and I told you all about

00:01:49.360 --> 00:01:52.670
the chemicals and the 50-gallon drums.

00:01:52.680 --> 00:01:55.149
It's very serious, what I saw coming

00:01:55.159 --> 00:01:58.190
out of Iran. Back when I

00:01:58.200 --> 00:01:59.950
started interceding for

00:01:59.960 --> 00:02:01.749
this, nothing was

00:02:01.759 --> 00:02:03.630
in the news about Iran wanting to

00:02:03.640 --> 00:02:05.709
do anything. Now they're saying they're

00:02:05.719 --> 00:02:07.670
at war. Iran is saying

00:02:07.670 --> 00:02:07.680
they're

00:02:07.680 --> 00:02:09.669
not going to do anything

00:02:09.669 --> 00:02:09.679
more,

00:02:09.679 --> 00:02:11.430
but

00:02:11.440 --> 00:02:13.790
they're liars;

00:02:13.800 --> 00:02:15.550
they're planning something.

00:02:15.560 --> 00:02:18.630
This is where I was in intercessory

00:02:18.640 --> 00:02:21.229
prayer concerning this. I

00:02:21.229 --> 00:02:21.239
saw

00:02:21.239 --> 00:02:23.630
50-gallon drums of

00:02:23.640 --> 00:02:26.790
biological weapons coming into Syria,

00:02:26.800 --> 00:02:30.309
traveling on the border of

00:02:30.319 --> 00:02:33.070
Iraq. I

00:02:33.080 --> 00:02:34.790
watched the truck in the spirit realm. As I said,

00:02:34.790 --> 00:02:34.800
this thing is

00:02:34.800 --> 00:02:37.270
just like

00:02:37.280 --> 00:02:39.110
a

00:02:39.120 --> 00:02:40.949
powderkeg.

00:02:40.959 --> 00:02:43.070
It's going to get even more intense. I

00:02:43.080 --> 00:02:44.990
don't know exactly when, but

00:02:47.400 --> 00:02:51.309
we haven't seen anything yet.

00:02:51.319 --> 00:02:53.869
The Lord will protect His people. I

00:02:53.879 --> 00:02:56.390
believe with all my heart that we

00:02:56.390 --> 00:02:56.400
must

00:02:56.400 --> 00:02:59.190
intercede.

00:02:59.190 --> 00:02:59.200
There

00:02:59.200 --> 00:03:01.790
is

00:03:01.800 --> 00:03:04.710
a lot

00:03:04.720 --> 00:03:08.550
I've seen in the last 48 hours. I went to

00:03:08.560 --> 00:03:11.910
a prayer meeting that Pastor Steve

00:03:11.920 --> 00:03:15.110
was having

00:03:15.110 --> 00:03:15.120
early

00:03:15.120 --> 00:03:17.350
in the morning.

00:03:17.360 --> 00:03:20.190
He invited me, and

00:03:20.200 --> 00:03:21.710
I started

00:03:21.720 --> 00:03:25.390
praying as a leader.

00:03:25.390 --> 00:03:25.400
Suddenly—and

00:03:25.400 --> 00:03:29.350
this

00:03:29.360 --> 00:03:30.630
usually

00:03:30.640 --> 00:03:33.670
doesn't happen in groups, I'm usually in the

00:03:33.670 --> 00:03:33.680
privacy of

00:03:33.680 --> 00:03:36.350
my home—the Lord

00:03:36.360 --> 00:03:37.990
started taking me

00:03:37.990 --> 00:03:38.000
into

00:03:38.000 --> 00:03:40.630
visions of things that were coming.

00:03:40.640 --> 00:03:44.070
The Lord warned me in that prayer

00:03:44.080 --> 00:03:45.750
meeting of attacks on American mega-churches. I saw an attack on a church in Florida and another on a church in North Carolina or South Carolina; I don't know

00:03:45.760 --> 00:03:47.309
exactly

00:03:50.030 --> 00:03:50.040
which

00:03:54.760 --> 00:03:57.589
state

00:03:57.599 --> 00:03:59.429
this

00:04:02.949 --> 00:04:02.959
man's

00:04:06.200 --> 00:04:09.149
church is

00:04:09.149 --> 00:04:09.159
in.

00:04:09.159 --> 00:04:11.789
I'm not

00:04:11.799 --> 00:04:13.470
going to name any names because this is

00:04:13.480 --> 00:04:16.069
a public platform, but it's a

00:04:21.629 --> 00:04:21.639
mega-church.

00:04:25.520 --> 00:04:28.469
Then the Lord said it's

00:04:28.479 --> 00:04:31.670
not

00:04:33.720 --> 00:04:36.670
only non-denominational; I saw Baptist, Catholic,

00:04:36.670 --> 00:04:36.680
and Methodist

00:04:36.680 --> 00:04:38.230
churches being attacked.

00:04:38.240 --> 00:04:41.629
It was a

00:04:41.639 --> 00:04:46.150
terrorist event related to ISIS

00:04:46.160 --> 00:04:48.790
that was going to try to

00:04:48.800 --> 00:04:51.550
take place on Sundays at American

00:04:51.560 --> 00:04:54.350
churches. I don't know exactly when, but

00:04:54.360 --> 00:04:57.670
it would be strategic,

00:04:57.680 --> 00:04:59.749
involving

00:04:59.759 --> 00:05:02.350
cells

00:05:02.360 --> 00:05:03.469
that crossed the

00:05:03.479 --> 00:05:06.550
border.

00:05:09.919 --> 00:05:12.670
I saw attacks

00:05:18.440 --> 00:05:21.790
with

00:05:25.029 --> 00:05:25.039
explosives.

00:05:27.680 --> 00:05:32.550
Then I was shown

00:05:40.440 --> 00:05:42.350
professional Major League Baseball stadiums. They

00:05:42.350 --> 00:05:42.360
were trying

00:05:42.360 --> 00:05:47.270
to fly in drones—not huge military drones, but ones you could buy on Amazon—equipped with

00:05:47.280 --> 00:05:49.790
C4 to take

00:05:49.800 --> 00:05:52.430
out large crowds.

00:06:01.240 --> 00:06:02.830
They were using remote

00:06:02.830 --> 00:06:02.840
controls

00:06:02.840 --> 00:06:04.510
to fly into

00:06:04.520 --> 00:06:06.830
the stadiums and

00:06:06.840 --> 00:06:09.830
detonate them. I

00:06:09.830 --> 00:06:09.840
saw

00:06:09.840 --> 00:06:12.270
that

00:06:12.270 --> 00:06:12.280
in the

00:06:12.280 --> 00:06:15.710
vision—planned,

00:06:15.710 --> 00:06:15.720
strategic

00:06:15.720 --> 00:06:20.189
attacks

00:06:20.199 --> 00:06:23.870
in

00:06:23.880 --> 00:06:26.710
America.

00:06:26.720 --> 00:06:31.350
Then the Lord showed me an attack on

00:06:31.360 --> 00:06:35.350
Sydney Harbor at the big Opera House and

00:06:35.360 --> 00:06:37.230
warned me about

00:06:37.240 --> 00:06:39.230
something that was going to try to take place

00:06:39.240 --> 00:06:40.790
there. I interceded for that

00:06:40.800 --> 00:06:44.390
at Pastor Steve's meeting.

00:06:44.390 --> 00:06:44.400
I saw

00:06:44.400 --> 00:06:47.270
some kind of

00:06:47.280 --> 00:06:49.830
escalation. What

00:06:49.840 --> 00:06:51.390
I was getting in the

00:06:51.400 --> 00:06:55.390
spirit was that there was a previous major

00:06:55.390 --> 00:06:55.400
event

00:06:55.400 --> 00:06:57.230
where

00:06:57.240 --> 00:07:02.150
people were hurt or

00:07:02.160 --> 00:07:04.430
passed away,

00:07:07.639 --> 00:07:10.589
but it didn't get

00:07:10.599 --> 00:07:13.790
enough national attention

00:07:13.790 --> 00:07:13.800
or

00:07:13.800 --> 00:07:16.990
create enough fear. Terrorist organizations

00:07:16.990 --> 00:07:17.000
in Australia

00:07:17.000 --> 00:07:19.629
were still plotting

00:07:21.520 --> 00:07:25.909
to take out a major

00:07:25.919 --> 00:07:29.029
landmark of significance

00:07:41.000 --> 00:07:44.189
to

00:07:44.199 --> 00:07:46.909
show they're the bullies

00:07:46.909 --> 00:07:46.919
and

00:07:46.919 --> 00:07:48.629
want

00:07:48.629 --> 00:07:48.639
everyone

00:07:48.639 --> 00:07:51.830
to fear them.

00:07:59.960 --> 00:08:02.990
Then I was shown the

00:08:03.000 --> 00:08:05.430
Olympics, and the Lord warned

00:08:05.440 --> 00:08:08.189
me to pray for

00:08:12.720 --> 00:08:16.029
them.

00:08:22.440 --> 00:08:25.270
If you live in Paris,

00:08:25.280 --> 00:08:28.510
I've told you before I saw fires

00:08:28.510 --> 00:08:28.520
and

00:08:28.520 --> 00:08:31.670
