00:08:31.680 --> 00:08:34.389
attack against Paris and the Eiffel Tower

00:08:34.389 --> 00:08:34.399
with

00:08:34.399 --> 00:08:36.430
smoke

00:08:36.440 --> 00:08:39.670
coming up.

00:08:44.000 --> 00:08:45.870
I felt it was related

00:08:45.880 --> 00:08:49.430
to terrorist issues.

00:08:49.440 --> 00:08:53.590
I saw the President,

00:08:53.590 --> 00:08:53.600
Emmanuel

00:08:53.600 --> 00:08:56.790
Macron.

00:08:56.790 --> 00:08:56.800
I

00:08:58.750 --> 00:08:58.760
saw

00:08:58.760 --> 00:09:00.470
an

00:09:00.470 --> 00:09:00.480
attack

00:09:00.480 --> 00:09:04.110
on

00:09:04.120 --> 00:09:07.750
the aquatic centers

00:09:07.760 --> 00:09:11.230
