00:09:11.240 --> 00:09:15.069
for protection over the ceremonies

00:09:15.069 --> 00:09:15.079
and that

00:09:15.079 --> 00:09:18.670
all hidden things be revealed

00:09:18.670 --> 00:09:18.680
so

00:09:18.680 --> 00:09:21.310
there

00:09:21.310 --> 00:09:21.320
is

00:09:21.320 --> 00:09:24.550
no loss of life.

00:09:40.959 --> 00:09:43.150
I was

00:09:43.160 --> 00:09:46.509
bouncing all over the globe. The Lord

00:09:46.519 --> 00:09:49.670
was warning me about strategic things

00:09:49.680 --> 00:09:51.670
that terrorists were

00:09:51.680 --> 00:09:56.550
plotting. I

00:09:56.550 --> 00:09:56.560
saw

00:09:56.560 --> 00:10:00.750
a

00:10:00.750 --> 00:10:00.760
passenger

00:10:00.760 --> 00:10:03.790
train coming from

00:10:03.800 --> 00:10:06.790
Germany going into other parts of

00:10:06.800 --> 00:10:09.069
Europe.

00:10:09.079 --> 00:10:11.030
This train

00:10:11.040 --> 00:10:15.069
looked green, and it had

00:10:15.069 --> 00:10:15.079
explosives

00:10:15.079 --> 00:10:19.350
on

00:10:19.360 --> 00:10:22.630
it.

00:10:24.279 --> 00:10:26.630
These

00:10:30.160 --> 00:10:32.670
are the key

00:10:32.680 --> 00:10:37.069
things I saw in prayer.

00:10:39.440 --> 00:10:42.470
As

00:10:44.240 --> 00:10:46.790
an American, the visions of the

00:10:46.800 --> 00:10:49.150
churches and stadiums are

00:10:49.150 --> 00:10:49.160
serious.

00:10:49.160 --> 00:10:52.430
People should be watchful, not in

00:10:52.440 --> 00:10:57.110
fear, but aware

00:10:57.110 --> 00:10:57.120
of their

00:10:57.120 --> 00:10:59.590
surroundings even in

00:10:59.600 --> 00:11:04.310
church. Pray and obey. Plead

00:11:04.320 --> 00:11:06.470
the blood over

00:11:23.320 --> 00:11:26.110
your congregation. We have authority over

00:11:26.120 --> 00:11:28.710
those

00:11:30.839 --> 00:11:33.230
demonic spirits

00:11:33.240 --> 00:11:35.629
inside those terrorists. Bind the

00:11:35.629 --> 00:11:35.639
maneuvering of that

00:11:35.639 --> 00:11:37.590
devil

00:11:40.839 --> 00:11:43.910
and

00:11:46.519 --> 00:11:48.829
declare

00:11:51.000 --> 00:11:52.790
that

00:11:56.320 --> 00:11:58.710
no weapon formed against you

00:11:58.710 --> 00:11:58.720
shall

00:11:58.720 --> 00:12:01.269
prosper.

00:12:24.880 --> 00:12:27.990
We are in

00:12:28.000 --> 00:12:30.949
a very

00:12:30.959 --> 00:12:34.150
serious timeframe. Jesus Christ

00:12:34.160 --> 00:12:36.949
is coming, and the devil

00:12:36.959 --> 00:12:40.550
