00:12:40.560 --> 00:12:42.949
going on in the

00:12:42.959 --> 00:12:45.230
spirit realm

00:12:45.230 --> 00:12:45.240
and

00:12:45.240 --> 00:12:49.670
knows his time

00:12:49.680 --> 00:12:53.350
