00:12:53.360 --> 00:12:55.629
There will be a day when he is

00:12:55.639 --> 00:12:58.189
thrown into the Lake of Fire for all

00:12:58.199 --> 00:13:00.030
eternity.

00:13:08.920 --> 00:13:11.389
The season

00:13:11.399 --> 00:13:14.150
of Grace is coming to an end. We're

00:13:14.160 --> 00:13:16.150
getting ready for the

00:13:16.160 --> 00:13:18.069
Rapture

00:13:18.069 --> 00:13:18.079
and

00:13:18.079 --> 00:13:20.150
the seven years of

00:13:20.160 --> 00:13:21.389
tribulation.

00:13:21.389 --> 00:13:21.399
The

00:13:24.750 --> 00:13:24.760
devil

00:13:24.760 --> 00:13:26.910
is

00:13:26.920 --> 00:13:30.430
trying to bring forth the

00:13:30.440 --> 00:13:32.310
Antichrist

00:13:32.320 --> 00:13:35.790
agenda as quickly as he can. He

00:13:35.790 --> 00:13:35.800
has

00:13:35.800 --> 00:13:37.949
no power until the

00:13:37.959 --> 00:13:41.230
church is

00:13:41.230 --> 00:13:41.240
