00:13:41.240 --> 00:13:44.189
the Great

00:13:44.199 --> 00:13:46.389
Restrainer,

00:13:49.279 --> 00:13:52.749
the Holy Spirit who

00:13:52.749 --> 00:13:52.759
dwells

00:13:52.759 --> 00:13:55.590
inside us, is

00:13:55.590 --> 00:13:55.600
gone.

00:13:55.600 --> 00:13:58.069
We have the power to

00:13:58.069 --> 00:13:58.079
restrain

00:13:58.079 --> 00:14:00.949
the devil.

00:14:10.790 --> 00:14:10.800
This

00:14:20.680 --> 00:14:23.670
affects

00:14:29.720 --> 00:14:32.710
all

00:14:34.720 --> 00:14:36.670
Christians—Baptist,

00:14:40.079 --> 00:14:41.870
Methodist,

00:14:41.880 --> 00:14:44.310
Catholic,

00:14:44.320 --> 00:14:47.069
the

00:14:47.079 --> 00:14:49.710
whole

00:14:49.720 --> 00:14:52.310
Body of Christ. We

00:14:52.320 --> 00:14:55.790
all still love Jesus even if we don't

00:14:55.800 --> 00:14:59.710
