00:15:20.040 --> 00:15:23.269
I

00:15:23.279 --> 00:15:26.870
saw

00:15:26.880 --> 00:15:30.550
refineries being attacked by the Israeli

00:15:30.560 --> 00:15:34.710
government.

00:15:34.710 --> 00:15:34.720
Now

00:15:34.720 --> 00:15:36.629
that

00:15:36.639 --> 00:15:39.870
Iran has acted, are we about to see Israel

00:15:39.880 --> 00:15:42.910
strike those oil plants?

00:15:55.120 --> 00:15:57.430
Oil shot up like a

00:15:57.440 --> 00:16:02.829
rocket, and gas was over $8 a gallon

00:16:02.839 --> 00:16:08.069
nationwide on average.

00:16:33.000 --> 00:16:35.629
I had this

00:16:35.639 --> 00:16:40.990
vision two years ago. Last year, the

00:16:41.000 --> 00:16:44.069
Lord warned me

00:16:50.240 --> 00:16:52.110
to pray over

00:16:52.120 --> 00:16:54.230
Coachella.

00:17:07.720 --> 00:17:10.470
I've sat on things for

00:17:10.480 --> 00:17:13.510
five years before they

00:17:13.510 --> 00:17:13.520
appeared

00:17:13.520 --> 00:17:15.510
in the news.

00:17:15.520 --> 00:17:17.110
I'm still praying over the situation in

00:17:17.120 --> 00:17:19.390
Italy.

00:17:19.400 --> 00:17:21.470
A major volcano is going

00:17:21.480 --> 00:17:23.590
to go off and wipe out

00:17:23.590 --> 00:17:23.600
a

00:17:23.600 --> 00:17:26.470
coastal city. I

00:17:26.470 --> 00:17:26.480
saw over

00:17:26.480 --> 00:17:29.750
300,000 people dead.

00:17:33.400 --> 00:17:35.070
If you

00:17:35.080 --> 00:17:38.110
feel earthquakes

00:17:38.110 --> 00:17:38.120
or

00:17:38.120 --> 00:17:40.590
see

00:17:40.600 --> 00:17:42.750
smoke,

00:17:42.760 --> 00:17:45.470
get out

00:17:45.480 --> 00:17:47.750
because you don't have much time.

00:18:10.320 --> 00:18:15.390
I saw a huge tsunami wave.

00:18:18.159 --> 00:18:22.149
When Israel

00:18:22.149 --> 00:18:22.159
retaliates,

00:18:22.159 --> 00:18:24.590
there will be a lot of

